---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import ButtonCustom from "../components/Button.astro";
---

<Layout>
    <section class="py-20 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-center opacity-10 z-0"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10 mb-16 text-center animate-fade-in-up">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-cyan-900 mb-4">
                Our Story
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                At Codebrand, we don’t follow formulas. We create new rules to
                turn ideas into results.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div
            class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-24 items-center relative z-10 group"
        >
            <div
                class="transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:-translate-y-1"
            >
                <img
                    src="/photos/teamcode.png"
                    alt="Equipo colaborando"
                    class="rounded-xl shadow-xl w-full object-cover brightness-130"
                />
            </div>
            <div
                class="text-gray-700 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed space-y-4 animate-fade-in-up delay-200"
            >
                <p>
                    From the beginning, we knew we didn't want to be just
                    another agency. We don't compete by offering the lowest
                    prices — we compete by delivering the highest quality your
                    business deserves. We know time is critical for companies,
                    so we decided to make that our focus without compromising on
                    quality. We were born to solve real problems in the shortest
                    time possible with top-tier results.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Our story began with a clear belief: well-thought-out design
                    transforms businesses. And to achieve that, talent alone
                    isn’t enough — it takes vision, strategy, and a highly
                    committed multidisciplinary team with real experience.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div
            class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-24 items-center relative z-10 group"
        >
            <div
                class="order-2 md:order-1 text-gray-700 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed space-y-4 animate-fade-in-up delay-300"
            >
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-orange-500">
                    One team. One idea. One mission.
                </h2>
                <p>
                    We are six professionals with different backgrounds and one
                    shared mission: to help brands grow with purpose, design,
                    and technology.
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
                    <li>
                        <strong>Graphic design and branding</strong>: to create
                        strong visual identities.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Web and app development</strong>: to build
                        functional digital experiences.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>3D animation and rendering</strong>: to
                        communicate with impact.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Marketing and social media</strong>: to connect
                        with audiences strategically.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Promotional products</strong>: to bring a
                        brand’s essence into the physical world.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div
                class="order-1 md:order-2 transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:-translate-y-1"
            >
                <img
                    src="/photos/teamcode.png"
                    alt="Especialistas del equipo Codebrand"
                    class="rounded-xl shadow-xl w-full object-cover"
                />
            </div>
        </div>

        <div
            class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-24 items-center relative z-10 group"
        >
            <div
                class="transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:-translate-y-1"
            >
                <img
                    src="/photos/teamcode.png"
                    alt="Proceso creativo Codebrand"
                    class="rounded-xl shadow-xl w-full object-cover"
                />
            </div>
            <div
                class="text-gray-700 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed space-y-4 animate-fade-in-up delay-300"
            >
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-orange-500">
                    Why Codebrand?
                </h2>
                <p>
                    We work with companies that value design — those who
                    understand that customization holds greater value and who
                    prioritize talent, quality, and commitment above all.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Every project we take on is a strategic collaboration. We
                    dive deep, ask questions, research, design, rethink, and
                    execute. Our goal isn’t to produce more, but to <strong
                        >do it better</strong
                    >.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div
            class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-24 items-center relative z-10 group"
        >
            <div
                class="order-2 md:order-1 text-gray-700 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed space-y-4 animate-fade-in-up delay-300"
            >
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-orange-500">
                    Our Essence
                </h2>
                <p>
                    At Codebrand, what you see is who we are: a team that cares
                    about every detail, thinks before designing, and believes in
                    the power of well-applied technology.
                </p>
                <p>
                    We aim to be the partner that transforms your vision into a
                    visual, functional, and profitable system.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div
                class="order-1 md:order-2 transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:-translate-y-1"
            >
                <img
                    src="/photos/teamcode.png"
                    alt="Sesión de estrategia Codebrand"
                    class="rounded-xl shadow-xl w-full object-cover"
                />
            </div>
        </div>

        <div
            class="text-center mt-24 relative z-10 animate-fade-in-up delay-500 flex items-center justify-center flex-col"
        >
            <div
                class="max-w-3/4 text-center flex items-center justify-center flex-col animate-fade-in-up delay-500"
            >
                <h2
                    class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-cyan-900 mb-6"
                >
                    Are you looking for a team that thinks like you and works as
                    if your brand were their own?
                </h2>
                <ButtonCustom text="Hablemos" href="/contact" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
